title: Strike.Suit.Zero.Directors.Cut-CODEX
description:
CODEX PRESENTS:
 
                      Strike Suit Zero : Directors Cut

    Release Date :  4/2014                         Protection : Steam
    Discs        :  1                              Genre      : Action

  In the year 2299, an interstellar war rages on. In a bid to save Earth
  from destruction, you must take control of the Strike Suit - a
  revolutionary fighter craft with the ability to transform into a
  lethal suit of space armor.

  The Director's Cut is the definitive version of the game featuring
  a next-gen graphical overhaul, completely new re-recorded voices, a
  restructured campaign and additional content - including the
  Heroes of the Fleet campaign.


   - Extract
   - Burn or mount the .iso
   - Run setup.exe and install
   - Copy crack from CODEX folder to your installdir
   - Play

   NOTE: This game requires a 64bit OS and a DirectX 11 compatible
         Video Card !!!
         While testing we noticed, that this game is still buggy on
         certain system configurations

   Block game exe in your firewall to prevent the game from trying to go
   online ..
